        <p>
          <m>\bullet</m> Collaborate with epidemiologists and health researchers to validate approaches
        </p>
        <p>
          <m>\bullet</m> Submit methodology papers to top statistics journals
        </p>
        <p>
          <m>\bullet</m> Develop R packages and software tools for research community
        </p>
      </example>

