    <subsection xml:id="grades11-12-math-competitive-research">
      <title>Competitive Mathematical Research: National and International Recognition</title>
      
      <p>
        Students can compete in prestigious mathematical research competitions, potentially earning recognition at national and international levels.
      </p>

